blocks.subject: Draft- Notice of EnronOnline auction
raw_header: To: Julia White/ET&S/Enron@ENRON, Steven Harris/ET&S/Enron@ENRON, Susan
Subject: Draft- Notice of EnronOnline auction
text: Attached for your review and comment is a draft notice to TW customers of the
EnronOnline auction.  Inasmuch as I haven't been part of the development
process, please check this document carefully for errors and/or
misrepresentations.   To meet the timeline for this project, please provide
your comments back to me by noon, Tuesday, May 16.  Thanks.
